column1: Have you or someone in your household experienced any of the following as a result of the coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak

column2: Had to start working from home
column3: Had their school or university closed
column4: Had to stop or scale back work to take care of their children
column5: Had to stop or scale back work to take care of someone who had COVID-19
column6: Had to take a cut in pay due to reduced hours or demand for their work
column7: Was laid off or lost a job
